name: Next game in the dark
description:
The cats are waiting for the boss to start the next game because there is an Iranian proverb that says there is no parental policy. The subject of this work is created from the effects of life around us. What do you think is the next game?
The original size is 16 x 19 cm and 1075p.x & 1434p.x / The printing technique is on metal and on handmade linen paper.
